location.fullValue: The Knolls at Plum Creek Condos

data.description:
Step into a life of comfort and modern living in this stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhome in the highly sought-after Sawgrass Plum Creek community. From the moment you walk in, you'll be captivated by the recent upgrades, elegant paint, and natural light flooding in from the large windows. The main level boasts stylish hardwood floors and new baseboards, setting the stage for a welcoming yet refined living space. The kitchen shines with brand-new stainless steel appliances perfect for any home chef! The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated, with one fully remodeled to feature a new vanity, toilet, tub, tile, and mirror, while others have received stylish updates for a fresh look.

Each bedroom is a sanctuary of its own, complete with vaulted ceilings and fans for that extra touch of comfort. The primary bedroom also offers an ensuite bathroom for ultimate privacy and relaxation. But the perks don't stop there. This home comes with a 2-car attached garage and out front it opens up to a common outdoor area, perfect for getting to know your neighbors while hanging out on your covered porch. Pet owners will appreciate the easy access to a park and dog park right across the street. Plus, with close access to I-25, Douglas County Fairgrounds, and historic downtown Castle Rock, you're never far from events and entertainment throughout the year. As an added bonus, you have access to a community pool, so you can make the most of those hot summer days.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity—schedule your private tour today!
